 Text in the Context of Occupation: Towards a New Hermeneutics of Liberation |location=Bethlehem |publisher=Diyar Publisher |pages=11–27 |via=Academia.edu |ref=harv }}{{dead link|date=November 2017}} : {{cite thesis |last=Weaver |first=Alain-Rene Tanne |year=2012 |title=Mapping Return: Palestinian Dispossession and Political Theologies of Exile |url=http://media.proquest.com/media/pq/classic/doc/2876535351/fmt/ai/rep/NPDF?cit%3Aauth=Weaver%2C+Alain-Rene+Waltner+Epp&cit%3Atitle=Mapping+return%3A+Palestinian+dispossession+and+political+theologies+of+exile&cit%3Apub=ProQuest+Dissertations+and+Theses&cit%3Avol=&cit%3Aiss=&cit%3Apg=&cit%3Adate=2012&ic=true&cit%3Aprod=ProQuest+Dissertations+%26+Theses+Global&_%3D&_s=8AUxoCLyGEIuibEiD6zHNmnf9WY%3D |type=PhD diss. |location=Chicago |publisher=University of Chicago |via=ProQuest |ref=harv }}{{dead link|date=November 2017}} : {{cite book |last=Wessels |first=Antonie |year=1995 |title=Arab and Christian? Christians in the Middle East |location=Kampen, Netherlands |publisher=Kok Pharos Publishing House |isbn=978-90-390-0071-7 |ref=harv }} {{refend}}
